Tae-hee's younger brother.

8
00:00:52,094 --> 00:00:53,137
Our youngest.

9
00:01:06,859 --> 00:01:07,860
Grandma!

10
00:01:10,946 --> 00:01:12,114
I have a younger brother.

11
00:01:13,157 --> 00:01:14,408
