42
00:04:52,418 --> 00:04:54,253
It's Hae-an.

43
00:04:54,336 --> 00:04:56,046
Oh, it was you, Hae-an.

44
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:59,174
-Is your mother visiting?
-Yeah.

45
00:04:59,258 --> 00:05:03,303
