anything not to say yet!

73
00:07:19,398 --> 00:07:20,774
Little brother.

74
00:07:23,026 --> 00:07:24,027
Huh?

75
00:07:25,404 --> 00:07:27,156
That's Tae-hee's little brother.

76
00:07:30,993 --> 00:07:34,246
L... Little brother...

77
00:07:37,166 --> 00:07:40,085
