Do you know
how worried I was about you all day?

87
00:08:17,956 --> 00:08:21,210
I wondered, "Did something happen,
is she getting sick," you know?

88
00:08:31,011 --> 00:08:34,139
-Uh, if my grandma--
-Tae-hee.

89
00:08:47,569 --> 00:08:50,489
I saw the picture
on your grandmother's phone.

90
00:08:57,496 --> 00:08:58,622
Your little brother.

91
00:09:03,502 --> 00:09:04,503
I...

92
00:09:10,676 --> 00:09:12,803
