277
00:28:36,006 --> 00:28:40,052
Hello. I'm Yoon Seol-a from Bongcheong
Elementary, third year, third class.

278
00:28:40,136 --> 00:28:42,304
Yoon Seol-a,
why do you want to be a singer?

279
00:28:43,681 --> 00:28:44,723
Um...

280
00:28:45,433 --> 00:28:49,186
EONJU UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL

281
00:29:00,656 --> 00:29:05,077
