293
00:29:59,673 --> 00:30:00,799
Go ahead inside.

294
00:30:04,929 --> 00:30:06,764
-Hey, Eonni.
-Yeah.

295
00:30:07,056 --> 00:30:10,601
-I'm good at singing too.
