300
00:30:29,119 --> 00:30:32,081
I'd like that! I'll practice until then.

301
00:30:32,957 --> 00:30:34,041
Thank you, Eonni.

302
00:30:35,209 --> 00:30:36,210
Take care.

303
00:30:50,432 --> 00:30:51,809
